    "description": "VTOL VR是一款专为虚拟现实打造的近未来战斗飞行游戏。驾驶先进的多用途喷气式战斗机，用手拨动开关、按下按钮并操纵虚拟飞行控件。应对各种挑战，考验你的飞行技术、态势感知和战术策略。<br><br>不需要额外的硬件。只要你有VR设备和定位运动控制器，你就拥有了一个虚拟驾驶舱，可以伸手抓握操纵杆和油门、拨动开关、按下按钮，甚至在情况不妙时拉动弹射座椅手柄。<br><br>身临其境地体验紧张刺激的战斗、精准的垂直着陆、航空母舰行动、空中加油等各种任务。<br><br>使用内置的任务编辑器和地图编辑器创建自制任务，并与其他玩家分享。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可驾驶飞机</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/001451fb25606ff9467ba16b4e449827.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><li>AV-42C 倾转引擎垂直起降攻击/运输机<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/032cc773a8b98b11edcbb43cf0bbe380.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>F/A-26B 战斗/攻击机<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/8c821a8beb8565ce557d311781f32806.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>F-45A 隐身多用途短距起降战斗机<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/0d13c1d9a03cb495db4f3061d73185f5.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>通过定位运动控制器实现的完全可交互驾驶舱<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/15eb8c30c99466db5bfd775a9466fb8c.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>自制任务/战役编辑器<br></li><li>自制地图编辑器<br></li><li>包含Steam创意工坊，分享玩家自制的任务和地图<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/6ac801a241eed2e6abad60169518a017.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>各种可更换的装备——机炮、火箭、导弹、炸弹等<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/016ff7b79c98b57a70bac1450eb53a3a.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>近乎逼真的航电系统——抬头显示器、瞄准吊舱、多功能显示器、雷达、红外曳光弹、金属箔条等<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/9d9d10ad7df4ac1d58e057ead2ca4e62.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>头盔瞄准系统——转动头盔来控制瞄准吊舱、导弹导引头和机炮炮塔<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/86c865f08a4b10cde9a6e6c3b7c7dc62.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>弹射座椅——当情况不对时弹射逃生<br></li><li>逼真的飞行物理——升力、重力、推力、阻力<br></li><li>多样的任务——“故事模式”战役、自由飞行、训练/教程<br></li><li>可指挥的AI僚机<br></li><li>AI友军和敌人——坦克、火炮、地对空导弹、舰船、飞机<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/667970/extras/5768ea21fd69a4a690fa4d6837769426.avif?t=1732654698\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br></li><li>空中加油——说起来容易做起来难…<br></li><li>地面加油和更换武装<br></li><li>航母行动——弹射起飞，阻拦索降落。使用光学助降系统！<br></li><li>无线电通讯系统，联络僚机、空管、预警机、地勤人员（兼容Windows 10语音识别）</li></ul>",
